				</li>
				<li>
					<p>
						By plotting the points in <xref ref="T-act-circular-traversing-2nd-ex">Table</xref> and connecting them in an intuitive way, sketch a graph of <m>h</m> as a function of <m>d</m> on the axes provided in <xref ref="F-act-circular-traversing-grid">Figure</xref> over the interval <m>0 \le d \le 16</m>.  Clearly label the scale of your axes and the coordinates of several important points on the curve.
					</p>
				</li>
